s sites\n    cointasker.com\n        tu dois reussir certains taches pour obtenir des bitcoins\n    coinad.com\n        en regardant des pub\n    elbitcoingratis.es\n        en tapant ton code-bitcoin et en entrant des captcha    \n\nil y a des echanges a faire sur le bitcoin\n    comme 1000euro peut etre convertit en 100bitcoins = 100btc\n\nune qtte de monnaie = une cle qui est unique au monde\n    donc en passant la cle_monnaie c de meme que \n    passee une qtte de monnaie\n\nbtc est un reseau p2p par bcp de gens dans le monde\n\nbtc possede un cours\n    ex: 1btc = 500 euro\n\nbcp de societe sur le net accepte le bitcoin\n    virginmedia\n    des universitees\n\npour echanger des monnaie reels en bitcoin\n    t_en a besoin de mt_gox\n    \nmt_gox a ete piratee\n\nle bitcoin est tres cher\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nthere is a ledger in which u will know the qtty of money of every one\n	everybody will have a copy of that ledger\n	_\n	what is inside that ledger is sth like this one\n		2345654dfghgfd875	900					\n		5as9hgf23b			7900\n +----> nb3490adgh			25             ----> this is owned by\n |  	xc5098725dyuiu		99                      one person and            +---+\n |                                                  only that person have this|key+->+\n +----------------------------------------------------------------------------+---+--+\n |\n |  but someone may use another person account by knowing his key\n +--ifk--------+--------------+\n        when an|account number|is created \n               +--------------+\n            there is|private_key|which is generated with \n                +---+-----------+\n    +-----------+                          +---------+\nthat|private_key|will allow you to create a|signature|\n                                           +---------+\n\n\n\n',NULL,NULL,'2015-05-13 10:52:13'),(1141,'multibit',NULL,NULL,'\npath installation\n    /usr/local/Multibit-0.5.18/\n','2015-05-01 18:05:22'),(1142,'electrum install',NULL,NULL,'\nhttps://electrum.